{"tid":732013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB解散體育組　30人炒剩5個","createTime":"2018-07-06T16:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T12:01:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"001ac42ac3906fa86b32c411e5e5a0ce80e0f8c1","tid":732013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180706/20441640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180706%2F20441640&d=VBfUe0L1U1Z5uIZsl0533p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=382b5c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180706%2F20441640&h=35f42f20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180706/20441640</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月06日 <br />\n<br />\nTVB解散體育組　30人炒剩5個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180706/large/06ls1p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180706%2Flarge%2F06ls1p10.jpg&h=db39390e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「大台」繼續向「細台」之路進發！電視廣播有限公司繼日前傳出解僱TVBI部份員工之後，無綫電視亦大裁員，其中體育組宣告解散，30人炒剩5人，歷史悠久的節目《體育世界》將於本周六播放最後一集。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《體育世界》明播最後一集<br />\n<br />\n消息指，無綫助理總經理（非戲劇製作）余詠珊決定向轄下的體育組開刀，解散體育組約30人，全組30人只炒剩5人，該5名「生口」會撥入新聞組，而體育組主管就被提早退休，《體育世界》最後一集於明天播出，Mytv super體育台亦只營運至8月15日。受影響員工昨日已收到知會，今日正式接信。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向無綫行政總裁李寶安（圖）求證，他承認體育組解散：「無綫電視在2014年播放世界盃期間，面對嚴重盜播情况，而近期亦留意到盜版侵權活動有增無減。無綫電視將來購買和播放昂貴體育賽事會更加謹慎，並會在中短期間集中播放及報道港澳地區的體育康樂活動。<br />\n<br />\n體育科將併入新聞及資訊部，而製作部節目包裝小組的工作性質亦會調整，整合後會減少20多名人手。」<br />\n<br />\n曾任《體育世界》主持的鍾志光慨嘆說：「唉！聽到呢個消息好突然，有家庭負擔嘅同事真係大鑊！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者戴彩煥  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港大生闖教員室圖奪PCLL卷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n中大為超重港人免費驗癌"},{"pid":"ec3ca2b8134cae8e25a8385b8df2b35140c95160","tid":732013,"uid":23236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"痴撚線！根本係舖路俾CCTV接手！"},{"pid":"4d89dc380011d52d8b9d1dfd55934f2f39643054","tid":732013,"uid":25221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e6420c3571d1a7fb10639bd640380c3b52a5683","tid":732013,"uid":118120,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"TVB而家做既事同晚期既亞視一樣"},{"pid":"44aa79424620aa089daa82e23510e9db6ae42a8d","tid":732013,"uid":31841,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e6420c3571d1a7fb10639bd640380c3b52a5683","tid":732013,"uid":118120,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"TVB而家做既事同晚期既亞視一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"鬼咩,佢請果班高層咪就係搞到亞視執笠果班囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3bab8c57e2dbc7b273a29f5a88c510c2135c08","tid":732013,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"鍾仔連PARTTIME 都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n體育世界 首片頭曲好經典...........完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16a6365f0930e8b65e60d0f889477ea003f0c86","tid":732013,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e3bab8c57e2dbc7b273a29f5a88c510c2135c08","tid":732013,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"鍾仔連PARTTIME 都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n體育世界 首片頭曲好經典...........完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:31:40.000Z","msg":"更正係球迷世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3e28730c28fb066959a7ac70915b0751459cf8","tid":732013,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0